gitCommit.subject: perf(ci): switch to llama3.2:3b for faster inference
gitCommit.body:
perf(ci): switch to llama3.2:3b for faster inference

- Replace phi3:mini with llama3.2:3b (2.0GB vs 2.3GB)
- Increase timeouts for GitHub runners (180s/60s)
- Llama3.2 has better performance than phi3 for selector generation
